data.description:
AIRBNB IN CASTLE PINES with Income History

HELLO CASTLE PINES!!!  PGA IS RETURNING - AUGUST 2024

Home on .47 acres in Beverly Hills Subdivision in unincorporated Douglas County, adjacent to Castle Pines.  Easy access to I-25, less than 10 minutes to Rueter-Hess Reservoir or Park Meadows, 4 miles to Ridgegate Light Rail, 15 minutes to DTC and 4.9 miles to Outlets at Castle Rock.  NO HOA.  This beautiful, warm and inviting home is experienced when you step into the foyer with living area that has vaulted ceilings and a view of the mountains.  The living, dining and kitchen have hardwood scraped flooring.  The kitchen has soft close cabinets with quartz countertops and custom tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances.   The primary bath is equipped with a jacuzzi and tile shower.  The downstairs, walk-out basement has a separate entrance and drive that allows for plenty of parking for rv, boat or toys.  There is a space for RV parking in the upper area as well.  The downstairs has been completed to serve as a separate in-law or rental space with carpet and luxury vinyl flooring.  The family room in the downstairs is wired for surround sound.  The bathroom in the basement level has heated tile flooring and tile shower.   Enjoy frequent visits from deer and other wildlife in the area. The home and been upgraded and kept in pristine condition.  Your are within blocks of Starbucks, King Soopers grocery store, banks, library and many good restaurants.  The shared well is $150 for 2 months for 10,000 gallons.  This home has many outstanding features and will be the perfect fit for the new owners.
